    "Minimal, consistent single-column layout with clear primary task entry",
    "Plain-language copy with useful placeholders and empty-state guidance",
    "Visible focus styling and built-in error containers support basic usability"
  ],
  "top_issues": [
    "Low-contrast secondary text/status styling triggers axe color-contrast violations",
    "Loading and system-status feedback are subtle and rely on dimming or a small color dot",
    "Small checkbox/delete targets and limited preventive validation reduce usability"
